* belli bir sn'den baslatma;
avplay -ss <saniye>
* vidyo hakkinda bilgi vidyoyu baslattiginda konsola yaziliyor
Command-line options
In addition to the generic options that apply to all applications of the Libav project (see Libav ), the following are accepted:

Option	Importance
-x BREITE	Force display width
-y HÖHE	Force display height
-an	Disable sound
-vn	Disable image
-ss POSITION	Jump to the beginning POSITION (in seconds)
-t DAUER	Play DURATION second picture / sound
-f FORMAT	Force FORMAT
-nodisp	Turn off graphical display
A complete listing provides the manpage to avplay.

Commands during playback
Button	Action
Q ,  Esc	End
F	Fullscreen on / off
P ,          	Break
A	Changing the Audio Channel
V	Change video channel
T	Change subtitle channel
← /  →	10 seconds jump back / forward
↑ /  ↓	1 minute jump back / forward
* [Kaynak](http://wiki.ubuntuusers.de/avplay)
